{"tid":497791,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"東京行程點算好","createTime":"2017-12-13T07:07:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-16T00:30:46.000Z","uid":124343,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"f17960a18e60b7c3f5785be628d1784e5a9c57c8","tid":497791,"uid":124343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T07:07:57.000Z","msg":"小弟過多個星期第一次去東京<br />\n睇左好耐 都唔係好搞得清交通 又唔識日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求巴打幫手睇睇<br />\n同埋係咪無櫻花啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nday1<br />\nANA airline 05:30左右到羽田<br />\n換3日pass<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.klook.com/zh-HK/activity/1552-subway-ticket-tokyo/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.klook.com%2Fzh-HK%2Factivity%2F1552-subway-ticket-tokyo%2F&d=73bTbcxjpI%2Fr7VMQknwB%2F4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=c9026e9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.klook.com/zh-HK/activity/1552-subway-ticket-tokyo/</a><br />\n早:築地早餐(想問未CHECK IN得 行李放邊好)<br />\n酒店 淺草駅 放行李<br />\n午:唔知去邊好<br />\n晚:晴空塔<br />\n<br />\nDAY2<br />\n早:換酒店 青抵駅<br />\n午: 秋葉原/唔知去邊好<br />\n晚:1830-2030 秋葉原mario(無book導遊,求路線)<br />\n<br />\nDay3<br />\n早:銀座<br />\n午:濱離宮恩賜庭園/ 東京鐵塔 / 新宿公園(如有櫻花)/唔知去邊好<br />\n晚: 新宿/涉谷 <br />\n<br />\nDay4<br />\n早: 築地<br />\n午:動物園/水族館/皇居<br />\n晚:池袋夾公仔<br />\n<br />\nDay5<br />\n早:淺草和服<br />\n午:淺草和服<br />\n晚:池袋夾公仔/新宿/涉谷<br />\n<br />\nDay6:<br />\n早:新宿-&gt;河口<br />\n午:河口湖/邊到睇富士山好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n晚:溫泉酒店<br />\n<br />\nDay7<br />\n早:富士倒影<br />\n午:河口-&gt;新宿-&gt;木更津outlet<br />\n晚:木更津dinner -&gt; 羽田機場 (聽朝7點機)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求批<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7494a8e4c00c5ccf7891c3ed0b80e89cfd1b784c","tid":497791,"uid":632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T07:10:15.000Z","msg":"巴打獨遊"},{"pid":"95db0e530165b3debc8a3d58a470db94278