\n午:河口-&gt;新宿-&gt;木更津outlet<br />\n晚:木更津dinner -&gt; 羽田機場 (聽朝7點機)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求批<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"058c109e4bbb4c8ac05505d40f2fc32b225f0e66","tid":497791,"uid":44814,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T07:28:04.000Z","msg":"問有無櫻花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 笑左"},{"pid":"6b0f3c03c92b19c94795ad0e6bb0d9fee1d30033","tid":497791,"uid":51904,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T07:37:28.000Z","msg":"12月想睇櫻花?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53fdd05d0744d22a0ab6097ec1c769238322b070","tid":497791,"uid":56239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T07:43:16.000Z","msg":"櫻花三月尾開始開，而家不如博下紅葉仲有冇<br />\n<br />\n個人建議去晴空塔可以唔使去東京鐵塔，畀着我就兩座都唔上，上政府大樓望下個景算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去得銀座應該shopping買名牌？有7日不如抽一兩日去箱根/伊豆之類近郊行下"},{"pid":"e71f2991fce14dbb5e9e6703f7db3154835b591b","tid":497791,"uid":90000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T07:43:47.000Z","msg":"Day 3 朝早去銀座做乜鳩野"},{"pid":"ff7fef4b8cf25f014be60d3750757193c6a419ef","tid":497791,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T07:45:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Day 3 朝早去銀座做乜鳩野</blockquote><br />\n倒不如第一日去築地食完早餐行去銀座仲就腳"},{"pid":"e24fac4590c4d27f91fb4408ca8cf07821554d25","tid":497791,"uid":90000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T07:52:17.000Z","msg":"建議樓主可以去睇下聖誕燈飾<br />\n<br />\n汐留<br />\n六本木<br />\n表參道<br />\n目黑川<br />\n涉谷青之洞窟"},{"pid":"0942af9e6bd6b2db5b67cf759a748f7607cde985","tid":497791,"uid":121005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T07:56:14.000Z","msg":"去得淺草就去埋吉原體驗下啦"},{"pid":"320edb929eb0b118b9f93da3aa468b0753a518c8","tid":497791,"uid":90000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T07:56:34.000Z","msg":"記得目黑川舊年有櫻花色燈飾，今年唔知有冇，樓主自己做下功課"},{"pid":"2e3dd63e70b46fde72dc59d937b00f26a449c066","tid":497791,"uid":96486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T08:04:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>櫻花三月尾開始開，而家不如博下紅葉仲有冇<br />\n<br />\n個人建議去晴空塔可以唔使去東京鐵塔，畀着我就兩座都唔上，上政府大樓望下個景算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去得銀座應該shopping買名牌？有7日不如抽一兩日去箱根/伊豆之類近郊行下</blockquote><br />\n我都認同呀巴打，東京鐵塔除非你想去睇海賊王。<br />\n晴空塔我覺得都幾值得去既，不過好多人，條外國人排唔值得比多舊錢排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"599137bf188a1a197bebd63b92d766404e17a76d","tid":497791,"uid":53880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T08:46:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟過多個星期第一次去東京<br />\n睇左好耐 都唔係好搞得清交通 又唔識日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求巴打幫手睇睇<br />\n同埋係咪無櫻花啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nday1<br />\nANA airline 05:30左右到羽田<br />\n換3日pass<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.klook.com/zh-HK/activity/1552-subway-ticket-tokyo/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.klook.com%2Fzh-HK%2Factivity%2F1552-subway-ticket-tokyo%2F&d=73bTbcxjpI%2Fr7VMQknwB%2F4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=c9026e9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.klook.com/zh-HK/activity/1552-subway-ticket-tokyo/</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">上乘換案內check下每日要搭幾多程 有時只搭2-3程反而會蝕錢比佢</span><br />\n早:築地早餐(想問未CHECK IN得 行李放邊好)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">地鐵站有Locker 可以放足一日<br />\n放左行李就唔洗急住check in </span><br />\n午:唔知去邊好<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">築地附近就不如去東京站, 睇皇居 或者落汐留去濱離宮恩賜庭園</span><br />\n晚:晴空塔<br />\n<br />\nDAY2<br />\n早:換酒店 青抵駅<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">做乜訂到咁遠... 個站仲要冇metro</span><br />\n午: 秋葉原/唔知去邊好<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">朝早去上野動物園/横町或者淺草 再落秋葉原行</span><br />\n晚:1830-2030 秋葉原mario(無book導遊,求路線)<br />\n<br />\nDay3<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">池袋/新宿/涉谷一日過啦 明治神宮/御苑/水族館/行街夾公仔 一定夠行<br />\n行唔夠可以分多日出黎</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDay4 + Day5<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">築地冇野行 除非好想再去食野</span><br />\n兩日分別見建議落橫濱行一日<br />\n或者去台場<br />\n鍾意動漫之類就可以去三鷹,吉祥寺,中野果面行一日半日<br />\n<br />\n求批<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n印像中夾公仔池袋好似貴啲<br />\n之後冇意見<br />\n留意下有冇燈飾睇<br />\n六本目睇夜景都係好選擇"},{"pid":"6c4a079dddc3ec663d8348aac8654e2187478111","tid":497791,"uid":4587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T08:55:34.000Z","msg":"下星期都去東京<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打邊日飛？"},{"pid":"4a9243ad5fa9d51b033b8412185661e4c1813e69","tid":497791,"uid":81664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T08:57:09.000Z","msg":"我都係下星期去, 我D行程全部睇燈飾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88d409d57cba63ff42a2260643da33d2f896396e","tid":497791,"uid":57674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T09:00:34.000Z","msg":"早兩星期返黎<br />\n巴打櫻花就應該未有喇<br />\n紅葉就某啲地方仲有既<br />\n<br />\n東京鐵塔改為晴空塔會好啲<br />\n晴空塔個水族館唔好去 150蚊左右 1個鐘行晒<br />\n要去就去葛西臨海水族園，一出JR望到個大公園就有驚喜"},{"pid":"c633827b9e657ffbb905f7b49f3997dba2c330e2","tid":497791,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T09:04:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>記得目黑川舊年有櫻花色燈飾，今年唔知有冇，樓主自己做下功課</blockquote><br />\n中目黑 keep 住聖誕都會有。"},{"pid":"28fa782878496a13bc0400f68c86b8859d78e26a","tid":497791,"uid":124343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T11:30:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下星期都去東京<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打邊日飛？</blockquote><br />\n18<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63a3478f98f9cf59e251cdca86c3dfee2c3af296","tid":497791,"uid":129664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T13:33:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟過多個星期第一次去東京<br />\n睇左好耐 都唔係好搞得清交通 又唔識日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求巴打幫手睇睇<br />\n同埋係咪無櫻花啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nday1<br />\nANA airline 05:30左右到羽田<br />\n換3日pass<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.klook.com/zh-HK/activity/1552-subway-ticket-tokyo/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.klook.com%2Fzh-HK%2Factivity%2F1552-subway-ticket-tokyo%2F&d=73bTbcxjpI%2Fr7VMQknwB%2F4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=c9026e9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.klook.com/zh-HK/activity/1552-subway-ticket-tokyo/</a><br />\n早:築地早餐(想問未CHECK IN得 行李放邊好)<br />\n酒店 淺草駅 放行李<br />\n午:唔知去邊好<br />\n晚:晴空塔<br />\n<br />\nDAY2<br />\n早:換酒店 青抵駅<br />\n午: 秋葉原/唔知去邊好<br />\n晚:1830-2030 秋葉原mario(無book導遊,求路線)<br />\n<br />\nDay3<br />\n早:銀座<br />\n午:濱離宮恩賜庭園/ 東京鐵塔 / 新宿公園(如有櫻花)/唔知去邊好<br />\n晚: 新宿/涉谷 <br />\n<br />\nDay4<br />\n早: 築地<br />\n午:動物園/水族館/皇居<br />\n晚:池袋夾公仔<br />\n<br />\nDay5<br />\n早:淺草和服<br />\n午:淺草和服<br />\n晚:池袋夾公仔/新宿/涉谷<br />\n<br />\nDay6:<br />\n早:新宿-&gt;河口<br />\n午:河口湖/邊到睇富士山好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n晚:溫泉酒店<br />\n<br />\nDay7<br />\n早:富士倒影<br />\n午:河口-&gt;新宿-&gt;木更津outlet<br />\n晚:木更津dinner -&gt; 羽田機場 (聽朝7點機)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求批<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第一日好地地住淺草酒店，無端端做乜轉青砥？仲要行程又唔係近嗰邊，換完間遠啲既酒店跟住下午又返返去秋葉原係乜玩法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95dbbb3d097167f60d78ee87dc7838ce2acb1d99","tid":497791,"uid":162270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T13:44:41.000Z","msg":"名古屋可能真係仲有櫻花睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n頭盔)唔知完未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10e8cbc0de2c565d7fa93a2425c8f4da65d3c230","tid":497791,"uid":61529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T13:54:41.000Z","msg":"未check in都可以放住行李係酒店先㗎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0998e98a4086a5e2c7cb81109814f769f83f1a93","tid":497791,"uid":94978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T13:57:00.000Z","msg":"揾一日去輕井澤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93f5d0f6cfc81f9f2092105a33b4ec053881c910","tid":497791,"uid":152158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T15:50:38.000Z","msg":"上星期尾返<br />\n銀杏尚剩少量"},{"pid":"6d292dd278ebca1a3a279681821ce1cdd005ce40","tid":497791,"uid":124343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T16:19:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小弟過多個星期第一次去東京<br />\n睇左好耐 都唔係好搞得清交通 又唔識日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求巴打幫手睇睇<br />\n同埋係咪無櫻花啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nday1<br />\nANA airline 05:30左右到羽田<br />\n換3日pass<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.klook.com/zh-HK/activity/1552-subway-ticket-tokyo/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.klook.com%2Fzh-HK%2Factivity%2F1552-subway-ticket-tokyo%2F&d=73bTbcxjpI%2Fr7VMQknwB%2F4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=c9026e9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.klook.com/zh-HK/activity/1552-subway-ticket-tokyo/</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">上乘換案內check下每日要搭幾多程 有時只搭2-3程反而會蝕錢比佢</span><br />\n早:築地早餐(想問未CHECK IN得 行李放邊好)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">地鐵站有Locker 可以放足一日<br />\n放左行李就唔洗急住check in </span><br />\n午:唔知去邊好<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">築地附近就不如去東京站, 睇皇居 或者落汐留去濱離宮恩賜庭園</span><br />\n晚:晴空塔<br />\n<br />\nDAY2<br />\n早:換酒店 青抵駅<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">做乜訂到咁遠... 個站仲要冇metro</span><br />\n午: 秋葉原/唔知去邊好<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">朝早去上野動物園/横町或者淺草 再落秋葉原行</span><br />\n晚:1830-2030 秋葉原mario(無book導遊,求路線)<br />\n<br />\nDay3<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">池袋/新宿/涉谷一日過啦 明治神宮/御苑/水族館/行街夾公仔 一定夠行<br />\n行唔夠可以分多日出黎</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDay4 + Day5<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">築地冇野行 除非好想再去食野</span><br />\n兩日分別見建議落橫濱行一日<br />\n或者去台場<br />\n鍾意動漫之類就可以去三鷹,吉祥寺,中野果面行一日半日<br />\n<br />\n求批<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n印像中夾公仔池袋好似貴啲<br />\n之後冇意見<br />\n留意下有冇燈飾睇<br />\n六本目睇夜景都係好選擇</blockquote><br />\n感謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b424a83d59ea7257c6019317b03fd598302a9af8","tid":497791,"uid":158301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T16:22:51.000Z","msg":"day 1 咁遲去築地，想食邊間？"},{"pid":"3f14b543bbca955f735de3380d0f0f702f83100e","tid":497791,"uid":50980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T16:29:40.000Z","msg":"其實可能有冬櫻  不過東京附近好似都無    另外男人老狗一條友著和服會唔會柒左少少   有人陪一齊行就好啲"},{"pid":"ec4f0ba0010bdd81a227edbe7f16389cc04b6b2e","tid":497791,"uid":38195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T16:32:30.000Z","msg":"去睇燈飾啦<br />\n涉谷 汐留 六本木<br />\n如果星期六可以去埋台場睇煙火"},{"pid":"cf5829bfcbc5895bea97a521cabbd06d7cf9ff62","tid":497791,"uid":86602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T16:37:32.000Z","msg":"如果想睇富士倒影，朝早睇既話山中湖可以睇到成座富士山，不過留意返巴士既時間就真！但超推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/14/003643_c565a849996e7cd41da8856822df8c8c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F14